// ============================================================
// OPTIONS FLOW ENGINE v1 — Institutional-Grade GEX + Flow
// Phase 2.2 of Quantum Engineering Trading Pipeline
//
// PHILOSOPHY (Citadel/RenTech-inspired):
// Dealers must delta-hedge. +GEX = mean-reversion. -GEX = breakout.
